<h2>Categories</h2><br>

<h4>Market Place</h4>
<p>Marketplace is meant for buying, selling and giving away items.<p>
<p><b>Examples:</b></p>
<p>Sofa for sale <br> 
Giving away little kittens</p>

<h4>Borrow Items</h4>
<p>Here you can ask other users to lend thing for you.<p>
<p><b>Examples:</b></p>
<p>Borrow a hammer <br>
Borrow another guitar for the Guitar Hero"</p>

<h4>Favors</h4>
<p>Here you can find listings, in which help for various tasks is needed.<p>
<p><b>Examples:</b></p>
<p>Walking the dog<br>
Help with computer problems<br>
Activities that need more than one person (e.g. folding the sheets)<br></p>

<h4>Groups</h4>
<p>In group search you can search for more than one person at a time. 
This category can be used both for leisure and more useful tasks. Listings in this category usually don’t offer or ask for any payment.<p>
<p><b>Examples:</b></p>
<p>Searching for company to watch a movie<br>
Workers for community effort<br>
Searching for someone to play badminton with<br></p>

<h4>Rides</h4>
<p>This category is meant for searching and offering car rides, saving money and nature!<p>
<p><b>Examples:</b></p>
<p>You're driving to Turku tomorrow, and you could give somebody else a ride there too</p>
	
<h4>Lost Property</h4>
<p>Items lost find their owners here.<p>
<p><b>Examples:</b></p>
<p>You found an umbrella in a bus.</p>

